name: Temple Of Light
description:
From my Other Worlds Tour

Before the long voyage to a new world to begin Terraforming, each Caretaker crew member takes a trip to a Temple Of Light and at sunset receives a case that they take with them on their journey. It is mainly a symbolic gesture to give them comfort far from home to know that it glows with the light of their homeworld.
